passphrase = 'test'
expected_credential = 'credential'
credential_holder = CredentialHolder(passphrase, expected_credential)
new_credential_holder = RebuiltCredentialHolder(credential_holder.iv,
    credential_holder.passphrase_hash, credential_holder.encrypted_credential)
with raises(MismatchedPassphrasesException):
    new_credential_holder.get_credential('not test')
